	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non arbitror te aegrotare neque tabellionibus destitui, qui literas tuas, chare frater, ad nos perferant; miror itaque, qui fiat, quod integris 3 septimanis nihil scripseris.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego quoque nullas ad te dedi; non enim habui, quod scriberem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu vero hac excusatione, uti non potes, qui potuisses perscribere negotium 3 legatorum <placeName ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolano</placeName> redeuntium.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audio rediisse illos, sed sine <persName ref="p19166" cert="high">Francesco</persName>, qui traditus sit bestiis immanissimis inquisitoribus; unde plane mihi persuadeo iam cum eo esse actum.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sed servabit in se sperantem dominus, et saluberrimum est eripi ex hoc saeculo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si interea, quid actum sit in legatione, intellexeris, scribe, oro, id quid sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim dum expecto, quid de rebus, quae alibi fiunt, ad te possim scribere, ex nundinis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l491" cert="high">Argentoraten[sibus]</placeName> literas [ex] <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high">Anglia</placeName> scriptas 19. iunii accipio; sunt reverendissimi episcopi <placeName ref="l296" cert="high">Londoniensis</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Significat ille res <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Anglorum</placeName> bono et felici esse statu.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc demum turbas [seda]tas in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2524" cert="high">Scotia</placeName>; nam 2. maii ex carceribus e[vasisse] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18212" cert="high">reginam Scotiae</persName> in arcem <placeName type="auto_name">Hamiltoniam</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ibi d[uces] conscribit repetitura regnum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Adest gubernator et [copias] illas fundit fugatque maii 13.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Regina cum paucis effugit Cariolensem usque in urbem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830" cert="high"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l830">Angliae</placeName></placeName>; inde supplicat reginae Angliae, ut ipsam iuvet et regno restituat.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">At <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18212" cert="high">reginam Scoticam</persName> illam custodire; etenim petitur illa ad supplicium a gubernatore Scotiae; rursus petitur eadem a <persName type="citizen_name">rege Galliae</persName> ad liberationem.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" cert="high">Regina Angliae</persName> neutris illam adhuc concessit.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid futurum sit, brevi audiemus.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgio</placeName> post stragem clademve acceptam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName> furit dux Albanus impatientia infortunii; dicitur enim insignes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorumque</placeName> duces ibi cecidisse.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ergo <placeName ref="l1284" cert="high">Bruxellae</placeName> iunii 5. obtruncare iubet nobiles et heroas <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgas</placeName> olim captos plerosque, <persName type="auto_name">Egmondanum</persName>, <persName type="auto_name">Hornum</persName>, comites <placeName type="auto_name">Battenburgenses</placeName>, d. a <persName type="auto_name">Wyllers</persName> ac circiter 50, inter quos intercepit etiam iuvenes aliquot annorum forte 15, heroum filios.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iis confectis cum 17 vexillis progreditur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Antverpiam</placeName> ibidem quoque mactaturus; verum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15" cert="high">Antverpiae</placeName> accepit nuncium, unde vehementer dicitur contristatus.</s>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neminem ergo ibi occidit, sed 4. die, ex quo appulit, recessit <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l185">Groningam</placeName> versus omnibus praesidiis eo confluere iussis.</s>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicitur autem rursus pugnatum, antea scilicet et priusquam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l15">Antverpia</placeName> ille sit profectus, levibus proeliis, in quibus ceciderint circiter 600 <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName>; Wallonum signa 13 et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l185">Groningam</placeName> sese dedidisse principi Uranio et fratri, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20180">Ludovico Nassoviensi</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicuntur item novae copiae accedere ad principem et duo millia equitum Germanorum ad ducem Albanum.</s>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Putant omnes copiis signisque collatis confligendum aut nunc esse pugnatum.</s>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De qua re si quid certi accepero, alias ad te perscribam.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc te bene valere opto.</s>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutabis d. d.d consules, d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p1770">Carolum</persName>, d.  <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontisellam</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20473">Ganthnerum</persName> et omnes nostros.</s>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Iterum iterumque vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 23. iulii 1568.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="29" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> senior tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="30" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Tobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino et fratri meo colendo et dilecto.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="31" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
